    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Amrita Daftary</title>
    <description>Amrita Daftary is assistant professor (research) at McGill University, Montreal, and a researcher at the McGill International TB Centre. She is an expert in qualitative research and the social and behavioral contexts of tuberculosis, particularly drug-resistant TB, and TB-HIV coinfection in resource-limited settings. Follow her @DaftaryAmrita.
 
</description>
